        <headline>Warning to Sheep Graziers for Mid North, Mount Lofty Ranges, Kangaroo Island, Upper South East and Lower South East forecast districts</headline>
        <description>Sheep graziers are warned that cold temperatures, rain and showers and westerly winds are expected during Saturday. Areas likely to be affected include the Mount Lofty Ranges forecast district and parts of the Kangaroo Island, Mid North, Upper South East and Lower South East forecast districts. There is a risk of losses of lambs and sheep exposed to these conditions.</description>
